[[ C99 Project - Breakout, by Onuelito ]]

-[ Build Requirements ]-

 Library used 	: {OpenGL, X11}
 OpenGL Version : 3.0
 GLX Version	: 1.4

-[ Compiling ]-

 Use the `make` command in the root project directory then run the executable.


-[ Summary ]-

 The goal of this project was to make a light, portable and easy to compile game for GNU/Linux as
 well as to challenge myself.


